									.col-md-12
										p.number 3.
					.col-md-5
						.pillar#employ
							h4 How we help Moms
							p.opt-pillar-desc
								.row.mt.step-row
									.col-md-12
										p.step Sign up to become an Athena Mom, search our database of awesome projects and apply to those that interest you
								.row.mt.step-row
									.col-md-12
										p.step When selected, work with the business to agree on check-ins and deadlines that work for both of you
								.row.mt.step-row
									.col-md-12
										p.step Complete the project, earning the sense of fulfillment that comes from being back at work, building and sharpening skills and receiving compensation
					.col-md-5
						.pillar#empower
